   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">This protocol applies to all Space employees, contractors and visitors, and all operations including manufacturing facilities, technical centers, offices &amp; administrative buildings. All sites in all regions are expected to develop site specific procedures to comply with this protocol.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">This protocol identifies the minimum requirements associated with guarding for machines, plant and equipment.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Requirements apply to machines, plant and equipment used in the workplace to perform functions which include but not limited to cutting, drilling, punching, grinding, pressing, forming, hammering, joining, molding, combining, mixing, sorting, packaging and assembling. The protocol also applies to machines used in for routine and non-routine activities.</li>
